## 🔧 Plugins Required

Add in `build.gradle (app)`:

```gradle
plugins {
    id 'com.android.application'
    id 'org.jetbrains.kotlin.android'
    id 'kotlin-kapt'
    id 'com.google.dagger.hilt.android'
