## ⚠️ Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| Gradle sync failed | File → Invalidate Caches → Restart |
| Kapt error | Ensure JDK 17 is set in Project Structure |
| WorkManager not firing | Disable battery optimization for the app |
| Room DB crash on reboot | Check if all DAOs are properly annotated |
| Emulator slow | Enable Hardware Acceleration (HAXM/AMD Hypervisor) |

